    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-1a' );" name="009-1a" class="pb">[009-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:189'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='189:209'>　經禮補逸卷九　　　　元　汪克寛　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='209:215'>　　嘉禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='215:223'>　　　飲食禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='223:246'>大宗伯以飲食之禮親宗族兄弟小宗伯掌三族之别</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='246:269'>以辨親踈大僕王燕飲則相其法小臣饗食掌事如大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='269:292'>僕之法鍾師凡饗食奏燕樂鎛師凡祭祀鼔其金奏之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='292:315'>樂饗食亦如之籥師祭祀則鼓羽籥之舞饗食則亦如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='315:341'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-1b' );" name="009-1b" class="pb">[009-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='341:364'>之文王世子若公與族燕則異姓為賔膳宰為主人公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='364:387'>與父兄齒族食世降一等公與族燕則以齒而孝弟之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='387:404'>道達矣其族食世降一等親親之殺也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='404:427'>　愚謂盛哉先王之禮也其本在於養性防欲其用在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='427:450'>　於視聽言動周旋揖遜之間使人之視聽言動周旋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='450:473'>　揖遜一於禮則安有放其邪心驕奢淫佚蕩而莫之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='473:496'>　節者哉不放其邪心不驕奢淫佚蕩而莫之節則禍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='496:519'>　亂可息孝弟可行治教可興其立意微其為法逺矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='519:545'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-2a' );" name="009-2a" class="pb">[009-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='545:568'>　故設其器備其物辨其數立其文以待其有事者其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='568:591'>　用則在乎視聽言動周旋揖遜之間而已然孝弟莫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='591:614'>　始於親親親親之心無所不用則燕之之禮不得而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='614:637'>　廢焉燕之之禮不得而廢則設其器備其物辨其數</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='637:660'>　立其文以待其有事者於是而用之也是故莫尊乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='660:683'>　君也君雖尊不以位加於父兄燕序必以齒者達乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='683:706'>　孝弟之道也莫親乎同姓也然親親不可以無殺燕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='706:729'>　則族人世降一等焉凡燕之禮必主賔以備酬酢而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='729:755'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-2b' );" name="009-2b" class="pb">[009-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='755:778'>　族燕之賔主則異姓與膳宰為之者篤親親之道也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='778:801'>　夫飲食口腹之欲也而必節之以禮則驕奢淫佚平</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='801:824'>　而無過也歌舞耳目之欲也而必和之以樂則言動</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='824:847'>　揖遜易而無乖也莫不由親以篤乎恩有恩以著乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='847:870'>　愛有愛以盡其禮盡其禮則言動視聽周旋揖遜之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='870:893'>　間不徒接乎耳目所以服習而安之者自得於養性</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='893:916'>　防欲之幾也雖然不特宗族兄弟之親也逺而異姓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='916:939'>　諸侯之君臣以至於蠻貊夷狄之邦皆由是禮之行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='939:965'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-3a' );" name="009-3a" class="pb">[009-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='965:988'>　故人說而天下服矣人說而天下服則禍亂何由作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='988:1011'>　苟禍亂不作則孝弟行而治教興矣此乃先王之所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1011:1030'>　以為燕也嗚呼於此可以觀其禮之盛矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1030:1063'>月令季冬之月命樂師大合吹而罷<span class='krp-note'>注嵗将終與族人/大飲作樂於大寢</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1063:1091'><span class='krp-note'>以綴/恩也</span>王居明堂禮季冬命國為酒以合三族大傳上治</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1091:1117'>祖禰下治子孫旁治昆弟合族以食序以昭繆<span class='krp-note'>穆/</span>别之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1117:1126'>以禮義人道竭矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1126:1149'>　愚案此言繼祖收族之禮故有上治下治旁治之道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1149:1175'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-3b' );" name="009-3b" class="pb">[009-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1175:1198'>　以正其恩之隆殺屬之戚䟽也蓋合族以食使之有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1198:1221'>　所同而尊卑之禮一序於昭穆使之有所異而親踈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1221:1244'>　之義明如此則皆有禮義之别而人之道盡於此矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1244:1267'>　抑嘗論之大宗無子則族人以支子為之後為所後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1267:1290'>　服斬衰三年而降本親父母為期何也蓋於所後者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1290:1313'>　以尊服服之又為降已親之服所以明所後者之為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1313:1336'>　重而於大宗者上以繼祖下以収族不可以絶此聖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1336:1359'>　人制禮之意也或謂為人後者當易其父母之名從</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1359:1385'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-4a' );" name="009-4a" class="pb">[009-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1385:1408'>　所後者為屬而使之無二是未考於禮也蓋父母之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1408:1431'>　服當降使明所後者重而已非遂以謂當變其親也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1431:1454'>　親不當變則名可得而易乎名不可得而易則期服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1454:1477'>　雖除心䘮三年禮不可變也而謂輒可以絶其親乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1477:1500'>　不絶其親而能使其屬之䟽者相與為重親之厚者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1500:1523'>　相與為輕在以禮義明其内而不在於惡其為二而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1523:1546'>　強易其名於外也雖然降父母之服禮則有之矣絶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1546:1569'>　父母之名禮未之前聞也禮喪服齊衰不杖期章曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1569:1595'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-4b' );" name="009-4b" class="pb">[009-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1595:1618'>　為人後者為其父母服此其名之見於經未嘗易也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1618:1641'>　經既不易則凡為人後者生曰本親父母没曰考妣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1641:1664'>　禮之正也愚故因昭穆之别特附其說于下以俟知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1664:1672'>　禮者商確焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1672:1695'>詩棠棣篇儐爾籩豆飲酒之飫兄弟既具和樂且孺伐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1695:1718'>木篇伐木許許釃酒有藇既有肥羜以速諸父頍弁爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1718:1735'>酒既㫖爾殽既嘉豈伊異人兄弟匪他</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1735:1742'>　　　冠禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1742:1768'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-5a' );" name="009-5a" class="pb">[009-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1768:1791'>大宗伯以冠昏之禮親成男女禮記郊特牲冠義始冠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1791:1814'>之緇布之冠也大古冠布齊則緇之其緌也適子冠於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1814:1837'>阼以著代也無大夫冠禮古者五十而後爵何大夫冠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1837:1860'>禮之有諸侯之有冠禮夏之末造也天子之元子士也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1860:1883'>天下無生而貴者也繼世以立諸侯象賢也内則二十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1883:1907'>而冠玉藻始冠緇布冠自諸侯下達冠而敝之可也𤣥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1907:1930'>冠朱組纓天子之冠也緇布冠繢緌諸侯之冠也冠義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1930:1953'>曰冠者禮之始也是故古者聖王重冠古者冠禮筮日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1953:1979'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-5b' );" name="009-5b" class="pb">[009-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1979:2002'>筮賔所以敬冠事敬冠事所以重禮重禮所以為國本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='2002:2022'>也重冠故行之於廟行之於廟者所以尊重事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='2022:2031'>　　　三加冠禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2031:2054'>郊特牲醮於客位嘉有成也三加彌尊喻其志也冠而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2054:2083'>字之敬其名也委貌周道也章甫殷道也母<span class='krp-note'>牟/</span>追<span class='krp-note'>堆/</span>夏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2083:2121'>后氏之道也<span class='krp-note'>此始加/之冠也</span>周弁殷冔<span class='krp-note'>詡/</span>夏収<span class='krp-note'>此三加/之冠也</span>三王共</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2121:2150'>皮弁素積<span class='krp-note'>此論再加/之冠也</span>士冠禮始加祝曰令月吉日始加</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2150:2173'>元服棄爾㓜志順爾成德夀考維祺介爾景福再加曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2173:2199'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-6a' );" name="009-6a" class="pb">[009-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2199:2222'>吉月令辰乃申爾服敬爾威儀淑慎爾徳糜壽萬年永</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2222:2245'>受胡福三加曰以嵗之正以月之令咸加爾服兄弟具</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2245:2260'>在以成厥德黄耉無疆受天之慶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2260:2267'>　　　昬禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2267:2290'>大宗伯以冠昬之禮親成男女媒氏掌萬民之判凡男</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2290:2313'>女自成名以上皆書年月日名焉令男三十而娶女二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2313:2336'>十而嫁凡娶判妻入子者皆書之黨正凡黨之昬冠敎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2336:2345'>其禮事掌其戒禁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2345:2371'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-6b' );" name="009-6b" class="pb">[009-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2371:2394'>　愚案妻由判合故云判子者謂媵娣之類非聘之正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2394:2417'>　故云入夫國之男女至衆也年月日名自成名以上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2417:2440'>　皆書之及其判入又書日月以告君禮不幾於繁乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2440:2463'>　詎知先王之制所以厚男女之别正㛰姻之禮者其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2463:2486'>　馭人倫謹始之道至簡而要也夫自有别推而至於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2486:2509'>　萬物安則禮始於謹夫婦者繫於國之男女况於南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2509:2532'>　面天下之主哉是故古之君子未嘗不以身化也故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2532:2555'>　家人之義歸於反身二南之業本於文王世皆知内</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2555:2581'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-7a' );" name="009-7a" class="pb">[009-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2581:2604'>　而后妃有關雎之行外而羣臣有二南之美而不知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2604:2627'>　其謹始由於文王之身化也考之行露之詩野有死</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2627:2650'>　麕之作專言男女貞潔強暴不能侵陵彼乗約肆淫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2650:2673'>　丈夫尚不能安其守顧令天下之女子能之何其盛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2673:2696'>　也人徒見江漢之小國兔罝之野人莫不蒙化而善</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2696:2719'>　俗而不知其所以然者又本諸先王教化之行禮制</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2719:2740'>　之謹有以致之也於此可以觀禮而得其要矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2740:2763'>曲禮故日月以告君齊戒以告鬼神為酒食以召鄉黨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2763:2789'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-7b' );" name="009-7b" class="pb">[009-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2789:2812'>僚友以厚其别也郊特牲夫昏禮萬世之始也娶於異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2812:2835'>姓所以附逺厚别也告之以直信信事人也信婦德也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2835:2858'>一與之齊終身不改故夫死不嫁又曰昏禮不賀人之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2858:2878'>序也曽子問娶婦之家三日不舉樂思嗣親也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2878:2886'>　　　問名禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2886:2909'>媒氏掌凡男女自成名以上皆書年月日名焉曲禮男</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2909:2920'>女非有行媒不相知名</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2920:2928'>　　　納幣禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2928:2954'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-8a' );" name="009-8a" class="pb">[009-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2954:2977'>媒氏凡嫁子娶妻入幣純帛無過五兩曲禮非受幣不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2977:2992'>交不親郊特牲幣必誠辭無不腆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2992:3000'>　　　摯見禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='3000:3029'>郊特牲執摯以相見敬章别也<span class='krp-note'>案執摯所/奠雁也</span>表記無禮不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='3029:3041'>相見也欲民之無相䙝也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='3041:3049'>　　　親迎禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='3049:3072'>郊特牲男子親迎男先於女剛柔之義也天先乎地君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3072:3095'>先乎臣其義一也壻親御授綏親之也親之也者親之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3095:3121'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-8b' );" name="009-8b" class="pb">[009-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3121:3148'>也敬而親之先王之所以得天下也出乎大門而先<span class='krp-note'>去/聲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3148:3171'>男帥女女從男夫婦之義由此始也禮記哀公問冕而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3171:3194'>親迎不已重乎孔子對曰合二姓之好以為宗廟社稷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3194:3217'>主君何謂已重乎詩大明篇文定厥祥親迎于渭韓奕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3217:3240'>篇韓侯取妻汾王之甥蹶父之子韓侯迎止于蹶之里</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3240:3249'>　　　見舅姑禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3249:3272'>昬義夙興婦沐浴以俟見質明賛見婦於舅姑婦執笲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3272:3295'>棗栗段脩以見賛醴婦婦祭脯醢祭醴成婦禮也舅姑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3295:3321'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-9a' );" name="009-9a" class="pb">[009-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3321:3344'>入室婦以特豚饋明婦順也郊特牲厥明婦盥饋舅姑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3344:3359'>卒食舅姑降自西階婦降自阼階</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3359:3367'>　　　見廟禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3367:3390'>禮記曽子問三月而廟見稱来婦也擇日而祭禰成婦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3390:3395'>之義也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3395:3418'>　愚案禮舅姑存成㛰明日婦見舅姑共盥饋之禮此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3418:3441'>　成昬三月擇日祭禰者則舅姑已沒而婦見于廟也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3441:3464'>　非謂廟見後擇日又祭也婦人謂嫁曰歸故稱来婦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3464:3490'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-9b' );" name="009-9b" class="pb">[009-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3490:3513'>　詩謂之子于歸易言歸妹是矣曰成婦之義者謂生</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3513:3536'>　既不獲共養于舅姑廟祭亦如生存盥饋之禮明敬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3536:3559'>　事之當完故曰成婦之義也考之昬義婦見舅姑賛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3559:3582'>　醴婦婦祭脯醢祭醴明敬事自此始故曰成婦之禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3582:3605'>　也此雖存没不同亦皆互文以見義耳然則見廟必</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3605:3628'>　待三月者父母既沒為人子者謂婦之来以成絲麻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3628:3651'>　布帛以審守委積盖藏者其事也和室人當於夫在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3651:3674'>　中饋者其行也上以奉宗廟下以繼後世此又禮之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3674:3701'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-10a' );" name="009-10a" class="pb">[009-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3701:3724'>　重也職或不修有可去之事則不可以苟合也故必</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3724:3747'>　待乆觀其成婦之道而後廟告焉此亦致敬於其所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3747:3752'>　事也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3752:3760'>　　　賔射禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3760:3783'>大宗伯以賔射之禮親故舊朋友大司樂及射令奏騶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3783:3806'>虞大僕王射則賛弓矢小臣賔射掌事如大僕之法鍾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3806:3829'>師凡射王奏騶虞鏄師凡祭祀鼓其金奏之樂賔射亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3829:3851'>如之眡瞭賔射皆奏其鐘鼓典庸器祭祀帥其屬而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3851:3878'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-10b' );" name="009-10b" class="pb">[009-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3878:3901'>設筍簴陳庸器賔射亦如之大史凡射事飾中舍筭執</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3901:3924'>其禮事司常凡射共獲旌射人治射儀王以六耦射三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3924:3947'>侯三獲三容樂以騶虞九節五正諸侯以四耦射二侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3947:3970'>二獲二容樂以貍首七節三正孤卿大夫以三耦射一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3970:3993'>侯一獲一容樂以采蘋五節二正士以三耦射豻侯一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3993:4016'>獲一容樂以采蘩五節二正服不氏射則賛張侯以旌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='4016:4039'>居乏而待獲禮記射義故射者進退周旋必中禮内志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='4039:4062'>正外體直然後持弓矢審固持弓矢審固然後可以言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='4062:4089'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-11a' );" name="009-11a" class="pb">[009-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='4089:4099'>中此可以觀德行矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='4099:4107'>　　　祭侯禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='4107:4130'>射人祭侯則為位梓人張皮侯而棲鵠則春以功張五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='4130:4153'>采之侯則逺國屬張獸侯則王以息燕祭侯之禮以酒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='4153:4176'>脯醢其辭曰惟若寧侯毋或若女不寧侯不屬于王所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='4176:4199'>故抗而射女強飲强食詒女曽孫諸侯百福書曰侯以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='4199:4203'>明之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='4203:4211'>　　　燕賔禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='4211:4238'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-11b' );" name="009-11b" class="pb">[009-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='4238:4261'>樂記射鄉食饗所以正交接也射義古者諸侯之射也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='4261:4284'>必先行燕禮卿大夫士之射也必先行鄉飲酒之禮故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='4284:4307'>燕禮者所以明君臣之義也鄉飲酒之禮者所以明長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='4307:4330'>㓜之序也詩小雅賔之初筵發彼有的以祈爾爵貍首</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4330:4341'>篇以燕以射則燕則譽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4341:4364'>　愚案古者弦木為弧剡木為矢弧矢之利以威天下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4364:4387'>　見於易繫侯以明之載於虞書則射藝已見於黄帝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4387:4410'>　堯舜之時而其制度禮文則大備於周也何哉鄉三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4410:4437'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-12a' );" name="009-12a" class="pb">[009-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4437:4460'>　物之為敎也曰六德曰六行曰六藝蓋蓄德植行而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4460:4483'>　必播之以六藝射之所以為藝而次于禮樂者有足</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4483:4506'>　以成人之德行而觀其用舍者也古者天子以射選</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4506:4529'>　諸侯卿大夫士以中選之多寡為之慶譲盖亦主乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4529:4552'>　習藝觀德之成而不專寓於禦侮克敵之備也諸侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4552:4575'>　之射必先行燕禮卿大夫之射必先行鄉飲酒之禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4575:4598'>　此則飾之以禮所以明君臣之義長幼之序也其節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4598:4621'>　天子以騶虞諸侯以貍首卿大夫士以采蘋采蘩此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4621:4648'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-12b' );" name="009-12b" class="pb">[009-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4648:4671'>　則飾之以樂又所以養人之德使之周還中禮而各</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4671:4694'>　不失其節之志也故明乎此則事功成而德行立矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4694:4717'>　事功成而德行立則暴亂不作暴亂不作則身安而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4717:4740'>　國家可保矣學者於此念始生桑弧蓬矢六以射天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4740:4763'>　地四方必先有志於其所事勉乎心之所得身之所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4763:4786'>　存事之所習以趨乎進德之階窮理之地而不愧於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4786:4802'>　為男子者噫豈維射哉因并釋之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4802:4810'>　　　燕饗禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4810:4837'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-13a' );" name="009-13a" class="pb">[009-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4837:4860'>大宗伯以燕饗之禮親四方之賔客籩人賔客之事共</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4860:4883'>其薦脩之籩實醢人賔客之禮共醢五十甕醯人賔客</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4883:4906'>之禮共醯五十甕外府凡賔客共其財用之幣齎大司</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4906:4929'>徒大賔客令野脩道委積封人凡賔客則飾其牛牲牛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4929:4952'>人凡賔客之事共其牢禮積膳之牛司門凡四方之賔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4952:4975'>客造焉則以告委人賔客共其芻薪澤虞凡賔客共澤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4975:4998'>物囿人凡賔客共其生獸死獸之物場人凡賔客共其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4998:5022'>𤓰蓏鬱人掌賔客之祼事和鬱鬯以實彞而陳之司服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='5022:5049'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-13b' );" name="009-13b" class="pb">[009-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='5049:5072'>凡賔客共其衣服而奉之典瑞凡賔客之事共其玉器</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='5072:5095'>而奉之鍾師凡饗食奏燕樂旄人凡賔客舞燕樂鎛師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='5095:5118'>凡祭祀鼓其金奏之樂饗食亦如之籥師祭祀則鼔羽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='5118:5143'>籥之舞賓客饗食則亦如之司干祭祀舞者既陳則授舞器</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='5143:5166'>賔饗亦如之鞮鞻氏祭祀則龡而舞之燕亦如之典庸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='5166:5189'>器祭祀帥其屬而設筍簴陳庸器饗食亦如之司常掌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='5189:5212'>九旗之物名各有屬凡祭祀各建其旗賔客亦如之大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='5212:5235'>司馬饗食羞牲魚授其祭小司馬饗射掌其事如大司</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='5235:5262'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-14a' );" name="009-14a" class="pb">[009-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='5262:5285'>馬之法量人凡饗賔制其從獻脯燔之數量羊人凡賔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='5285:5308'>客共其法羊射鳥氏掌祭祀以弓矢歐烏鳶凡賔客亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='5308:5331'>如之服不氏賔客之事則抗皮射人賔客則作卿大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='5331:5354'>從司士凡賔客作士從諸子凡賔客作羣子從旅賁氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='5354:5377'>掌執戈盾凡賔客則服而趨大僕王燕飲則相其法正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='5377:5400'>眡燕朝則正位掌擯相王不眡朝則辭於三公及孤卿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='5400:5423'>小臣正王之燕服位王之燕出入則前驅士師王燕出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='5423:5446'>入則前驅而辟掌客掌四方賔客之牢禮飲食之等數</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='5446:5473'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-14b' );" name="009-14b" class="pb">[009-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='5473:5496'>凡諸侯之禮上公五積皆眡飱牽三問皆脩飱五牢食</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='5496:5519'>四十簠十豆四十鉶四十有二壺四十鼎簋十有二牲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5519:5542'>三十有六皆陳饔餼九牢其死牢如飱之陳牽四牢米</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='5542:5565'>百有二十筥醯醢百有二十甕車皆陳車米眡生牢牢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='5565:5588'>十車車秉有五籔車禾眡死牢牢十車車三秅芻薪倍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='5588:5611'>禾皆陳乗禽日九十雙殷膳大牢以及歸三饗三食三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='5611:5634'>燕若弗酌則以幣致之侯伯四積皆眡飱牽再問皆脩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5634:5657'>飱四牢食三十有二簠八豆三十有二鉶二十有八壺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='5657:5684'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-15a' );" name="009-15a" class="pb">[009-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='5684:5707'>三十有二鼎簋十有二腥二十有七皆陳饔餼七牢其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='5707:5729'>死牢如飱之陳牽三牢米百筥醯醢百甕皆陳米三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='5729:5752'>十車禾四十車芻薪倍禾皆陳乗禽日七十雙殷膳大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='5752:5775'>牢三饗再食再燕子男三積皆眡飱牽一問以脩飱三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='5775:5798'>牢食二十有四簠六豆二十有四鉶十有八壺二十有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='5798:5821'>四鼎簋十有二牲十有八皆陳饔餼五牢其死牢如飱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='5821:5844'>之陳牽二牢米八十筥醯醢八十甕皆陳米二十車禾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='5844:5867'>三十車芻薪倍禾皆陳乗禽日五十雙一饗一食一燕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='5867:5894'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-15b' );" name="009-15b" class="pb">[009-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='5894:5917'>凡諸侯之卿大夫士為國客則如其介之禮以待之詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='5917:5940'>湛露厭厭夜飲在宗載考彤弓鍾鼓既設一朝饗之鹿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='5940:5963'>鳴我有㫖酒以燕樂嘉賔之心春秋莊公四年夫人饗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='5963:5970'>齊侯于祝丘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='5970:5993'>　愚案春秋傳晉侯饗齊侯宋公饗晉侯楚子饗公小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='5993:6016'>　邾子郯子来朝公與之燕公饗宰周公范宣子饗晉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='6016:6039'>　六卿于蒲圃寗俞華耦来公與之燕至鄭伯饗王王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='6039:6062'>　饗晉侯經皆不書而書夫人饗齊侯則以其非禮也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='6062:6089'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-16a' );" name="009-16a" class="pb">[009-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='6089:6097'>　　　餼獻禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='6097:6120'>掌客掌四方賔客之餼獻飲食之等數上公之禮羣介</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='6120:6143'>行人宰史皆有牢及歸凡介行人宰史皆有飱饔餼以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='6143:6166'>其爵等為之牢禮之陳數唯上介有禽獻夫人致禮八</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='6166:6189'>壺八豆八籩膳大牢致饗大牢食大牢卿皆見以羔膳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='6189:6212'>大牢侯伯凡介行人宰史皆有飱饔餼以其爵等為之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='6212:6235'>禮唯上介有禽獻夫人致禮八壺八豆八籩膳大牢致</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='6235:6258'>饗大牢卿皆見以羔膳特牛子男凡介行人牢史皆有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='6258:6285'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-16b' );" name="009-16b" class="pb">[009-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='6285:6308'>飱饔餼以其爵等為之禮唯上介有禽獻夫人致禮六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='6308:6326'>壺六豆六籩膳視致饗親見卿皆膳特牛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='6326:6334'>　　　擯相禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='6334:6357'>司儀掌九儀之賔客擯相之禮以詔儀容辭令揖譲之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='6357:6380'>節凡諸公相為賔主國五積三問皆三辭拜受皆旅擯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='6380:6403'>主君郊勞交擯三辭及將幣交擯三辭車逆拜辱賔車</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='6403:6426'>進荅拜三揖三譲毎門止一相及廟唯上相入賔三揖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='6426:6449'>三譲登再拜授幣及出車送三請三進再拜賔三還三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='6449:6476'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-17a' );" name="009-17a" class="pb">[009-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='6476:6499'>辭告辟諸公之臣相為國客則三積皆三辭拜受及大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='6499:6522'>夫郊勞旅擯三辭拜辱三譲登聽命下拜登受賔使者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='6522:6545'>如初之儀及將幣旅擯三辭拜逆客辟三揖每門止一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='6545:6568'>相及廟唯君相入三譲客登拜客三辟授幣下出大僕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='6568:6591'>王燕飲則相其法王眡燕朝則正位掌擯相玉藻小國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='6591:6614'>之君曰孤擯者亦曰孤上大夫曰下臣擯者曰寡君之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='6614:6637'>老下大夫自名擯者曰寡大夫公士擯則曰寡大夫寡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='6637:6660'>君之老大夫有所徃必與公士為擯也聘義卿為上擯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='6660:6687'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-17b' );" name="009-17b" class="pb">[009-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='6687:6710'>大夫為承擯士為紹擯三譲而後傳命三譲而後入廟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='6710:6733'>門三揖而後至階三譲而後升所以致尊譲也禮器禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='6733:6746'>有擯詔樂有相步温之至也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='6746:6754'>　　　送逆禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='6754:6777'>訝士邦有賔客則與行人送逆之司儀王燕凡諸侯相</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='6777:6800'>為國主賔主君郊勞交擯三辭車逆拜辱三揖三辭拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='6800:6823'>受車送三還再拜及將幣車逆拜辱再拜授幣賔拜送</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='6823:6846'>幣及出車送諸公之臣相為國客及大夫郊勞旅擯三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='6846:6873'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-18a' );" name="009-18a" class="pb">[009-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='6873:6896'>辭拜辱及退拜送及將幣拜逆客辟授幣下出君館客</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='6896:6919'>客辟介受命遂送凡四方之賔客禮儀辭命餼牢賜獻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='6919:6942'>以二等從其爵而上下之凡賔客送逆同禮齊僕掌饗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='6942:6965'>食皆乗金路其法儀各以其等為車送逆之節環人掌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='6965:6988'>送逆邦國之通賔客以路節達諸四方聘義君使士迎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='6988:7011'>于境大夫郊勞君親拜逆于大門之内而廟受北面拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='7011:7034'>貺拜君命之辱所以致敬也敬譲也者君子之所以相</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='7034:7038'>接也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='7038:7065'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-18b' );" name="009-18b" class="pb">[009-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='7065:7072'>　　　勞禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='7072:7095'>小行人凡諸侯入王則逆勞于畿及郊勞眡館司儀凡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='7095:7118'>諸公相為賔主國五積三問再勞三辭三揖登拜受拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='7118:7141'>送郊勞三辭諸公之臣相為國客則三積郊勞三辭及</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='7141:7164'>禮私面私獻君勞客客再拜稽首君答拜致饔餼如勞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='7164:7187'>之禮曲禮大夫士見於國君君若勞之則還辟再拜稽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='7187:7190'>首</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='7190:7198'>　　　致贈禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='7198:7225'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-19a' );" name="009-19a" class="pb">[009-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='7225:7248'>司儀致饔餼還圭饗食致贈及禮私面私獻皆再拜稽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='7248:7271'>首君答拜聘義君親禮賔賔私面私覿致饔餼還圭璋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='7271:7288'>賄贈饗食燕所以明賓客君臣之義也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='7288:7311'>　愚案古者天子諸侯皆有朝聘之禮如大行人歳徧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='7311:7334'>　存三歳徧覜五歳徧省此天子所以撫諸侯之禮也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='7334:7357'>　春朝而圖天下之事時聘以結諸侯之好此諸侯所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='7357:7380'>　以事天子之禮也至於歳相問殷相聘世相朝此諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='7380:7403'>　侯邦交之禮也禮若國君親徃則大夫從王燕凡諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='7403:7430'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-19b' );" name="009-19b" class="pb">[009-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='7430:7453'>　公相為賔主國其擯相禮儀餼牢賜獻各以其爵之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='7453:7476'>　等相待也聘事既畢主國君親執醴以禮賔而遂有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='7476:7499'>　私面私獻之禮賔皆再拜稽首所以正交接之義也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='7499:7522'>　致饔餼還圭璋賄贈饗食燕者賓介就館主君使卿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='7522:7545'>　致饋於賓而還以執来之圭加於賄贈之禮也然則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='7545:7568'>　大夫從君聘而以己之私物覿見主國之君面見主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='7568:7591'>　國之卿大夫可乎夫執圭所以申信也將幣所以致</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='7591:7614'>　敬也私以庭實充于諸侯之庭則不敬也不敬是無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l349' data-llen='7614:7641'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-20a' );" name="009-20a" class="pb">[009-20a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l350' data-llen='7641:7664'>　王矣夫既從君聘禮無外交也外交是二君矣此皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l351' data-llen='7664:7687'>　非禮也注者謂若大夫執其君之命圭而專使則當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l352' data-llen='7687:7710'>　行私覿之禮以申己之信其說悖矣夫從君而来與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l353' data-llen='7710:7733'>　受命而聘一也一乃專二乃辟也考之太宰以八柄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l354' data-llen='7733:7756'>　詔王馭羣臣曰禄以馭其富予以馭其幸若相覿以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l355' data-llen='7756:7779'>　貨是人臣以利交也人臣以利交則二者胥失矣二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l356' data-llen='7779:7798'>　者苟失其不致於無禮奪亂者未之有也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l357' data-llen='7798:7806'>　　　賀慶禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l358' data-llen='7806:7833'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-20b' );" name="009-20b" class="pb">[009-20b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l359' data-llen='7833:7856'>大宗伯以賀慶之禮親異姓之國大行人賀慶以賛諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l360' data-llen='7856:7879'>侯之喜小行人若國有福事則令慶賀之玉藻有慶非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l361' data-llen='7879:7901'>君賜不賀士於大夫不承賀下大夫於上大夫承賀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l362' data-llen='7901:7909'>　　　脹膰禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l363' data-llen='7909:7932'>大宗伯以脹膰之禮親兄弟之國小宗伯饗食授祭大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l364' data-llen='7932:7955'>司馬饗食羞牲魚授其祭祭僕凡祭祀致福者展而受</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l365' data-llen='7955:7978'>之大行人歸脹以交諸侯之福春秋昭公十四年天王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l366' data-llen='7978:8001'>使石尚来歸脹公羊傳脹者何爼實也腥曰脹熟曰膰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l367' data-llen='8001:8028'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-21a' );" name="009-21a" class="pb">[009-21a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l368' data-llen='8028:8051'>　愚案受脹于社是諸侯助祭而授爼實也非助祭則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l369' data-llen='8051:8074'>　不授也如㐮王使宰孔賜齊侯胙是齊桓有奬王之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l370' data-llen='8074:8097'>　功而加以殊禮也今天王使石尚賜宜社之肉于魯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l371' data-llen='8097:8120'>　非縁助祭於京師曽是以為禮乎是故受賑禮也歸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l372' data-llen='8120:8127'>　脹非禮也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l373' data-llen='8127:8136'>　　　經禮附說</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l374' data-llen='8136:8159'>　周禮一書果為周公所作乎漢武嘗謂周禮為瀆亂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l375' data-llen='8159:8182'>　不驗之書何休又云六國隂謀之書歐文忠公謂周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l376' data-llen='8182:8209'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-21b' );" name="009-21b" class="pb">[009-21b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l377' data-llen='8209:8232'>　禮可疑者二蘇頴濵謂周禮不可信者三是皆論以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l378' data-llen='8232:8255'>　為非周公之遺制也然則周禮果非周公所作乎朱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l379' data-llen='8255:8278'>　子盖嘗以周家法度廣大精宻言之嘗以周公建太</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l380' data-llen='8278:8301'>　平之基本稱之又嘗以周公從廣大心中流出稱之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l381' data-llen='8301:8324'>　張横渠謂周公治周莫詳於周禮賈公彦序周禮廢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l382' data-llen='8324:8348'>　興又謂鄭𤣥徧覧羣經知周禮者乃周公致太平之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l383' data-llen='8348:8371'>　迹是則又明為周公所作也考之西漢志於周禮未</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l384' data-llen='8371:8394'>　之見東漢儒林傳乃謂周官經六篇本孔安國所獻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l385' data-llen='8394:8421'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-22a' );" name="009-22a" class="pb">[009-22a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l386' data-llen='8421:8444'>　隋經籍志乃云漢時有李氏得周官上於河間獻王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l387' data-llen='8444:8467'>　獨缺冬官一篇獻王購以千金不得遂以考工記補</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l388' data-llen='8467:8490'>　成六篇奏之孝武時盖有其書特未與五經例置博</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l389' data-llen='8490:8513'>　士耳至西漢劉歆始置博士遂盛行於世後世因有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l390' data-llen='8513:8536'>　周禮作於劉歆之說是則周禮作於周公而非他人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l391' data-llen='8536:8559'>　之制明矣然冬官何為而缺也經罹秦燄散帙之餘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l392' data-llen='8559:8582'>　與漢儒編録附麗之誤而始謂之缺也何以知其然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l393' data-llen='8582:8605'>　愚因考補散逸得之夫五官所掌曰治曰敎曰禮曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l394' data-llen='8605:8632'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-22b' );" name="009-22b" class="pb">[009-22b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l395' data-llen='8632:8655'>　政曰刑而冬官則掌邦士或坐而論道謂之王公或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l396' data-llen='8655:8678'>　作而行之謂之士大夫或審曲面勢以飭五材以辨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l397' data-llen='8678:8701'>　民器謂之百工通四方之珍異以資之謂之商旅飭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l398' data-llen='8701:8724'>　力以長地財謂之農夫治絲麻以成之謂之婦功此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l399' data-llen='8724:8747'>　冬官之大較也見考工記所載者其屬二十有九皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l400' data-llen='8747:8770'>　工之事而士與商農之職俱缺焉考之春官之中如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l401' data-llen='8770:8793'>　世婦内宗外宗皆宫中之職本屬天官而乃入之春</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l402' data-llen='8793:8816'>　官夏官之中如司士諸子皆掌士之職本屬冬官而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l403' data-llen='8816:8843'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-23a' );" name="009-23a" class="pb">[009-23a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l404' data-llen='8843:8866'>　乃入之夏官地官之中如司市質人㕓人賈師司虣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l405' data-llen='8866:8889'>　司稽胥肆長泉府此皆主於商土均草人稲人場人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l406' data-llen='8889:8912'>　司稼等職此皆主於農皆本屬冬官因其職與大司</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l407' data-llen='8912:8935'>　徒掌土地人民者相類乃以入之地官若是者謂非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l408' data-llen='8935:8958'>　編録附麗之誤不可也况小宰記六官六屬各六十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l409' data-llen='8958:8981'>　考之天官自太宰以下六十二地官大司徒以下七</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l410' data-llen='8981:9004'>　十九春官大宗伯以下七十一夏官大司馬以下六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l411' data-llen='9004:9027'>　十九秋官大司冦以下六十五何則冬官獨缺而為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l412' data-llen='9027:9054'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-23b' );" name="009-23b" class="pb">[009-23b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l413' data-llen='9054:9077'>　數不及五官皆盈而餘數過之理無是也他如儀禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l414' data-llen='9077:9100'>　有嗇夫之官國語有司商之官皆不載諸周禮此亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l415' data-llen='9100:9123'>　冬官之脫簡也要之見載於考工記者固為冬官之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l416' data-llen='9123:9146'>　屬然司空掌邦土居四民時地利職不止此當自大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l417' data-llen='9146:9169'>　司空小司空而下摭夏官之中掌士者地官之中掌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l418' data-llen='9169:9192'>　商農者與夫嗇夫司商之數并今考工記所載之工</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l419' data-llen='9192:9215'>　總屬冬官則不惟合於周官司空之所職與小宰六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l420' data-llen='9215:9238'>　官六屬之目而且周公制作之盛粲然溢著于編使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l421' data-llen='9238:9265'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '009-24a' );" name="009-24a" class="pb">[009-24a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l422' data-llen='9265:9288'>　人得以觀其㑹通而為太平典禮之全書也克寛因</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l423' data-llen='9288:9303'>　并録卷末以俟博古君子正焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l424' data-llen='9303:9306'>　</span><br/>
